title: Everymans Dictionary of Pictorial Art, vol 2 (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Everyman's Dictionary of Pictorial Art vol.2
J. M. Dent & Sons/E. P. Dutton & Co. | 1962 | ISBN: N/A | English | 422 pages | PDF | 84.4 MB

The aim of this work is to provide in concise form a convenient reference work on the whole realm of pictorial art; painters, periods, styles and techniques, from the earliest times to the present and in every part of the world where pictorial art has flourished
